<br>
Spell haste doesn't stack with bard song or spell effect haste.<br>
<br>
However, you may see two icons at once (for instance, enchanter haste will increase your speed, and a bard haste song will increase your ac/atk... but not your speed even though it also has a speed component).<br>
<br>
So you may think they stack, but they don't.  Verant has said this to be true... <p><center>    <b>Aktar Mythmaker <b></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=artillis>Artillis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/26/01 6:13:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How many FT items can a wizard get?</span><hr size=1> Aktar you read my post wrong, I NEVER said bard song stacked with enchanter spell haste.  <br>
