<br>
As regards to the haste.... <br>
<br>
Monks epics were made a SPECIAL case, where the epic adds things OTHER THAN HASTE.... The effect now stacks with other cast spells, but the monk is only hastened by the faster of the 2.... <br>
<br>
IE<br>
If you cast augment on a monk with epic haste on, it will use the haste from the epic and the stats from augment...<br>
<br>
If you cast Shissar on a monk with epic haste on, it will use the haste from Shissar and the stats from the epic...<br>
<br>
the haste doesnt stack off 2 spells..... <p>Mandoman Mischieflover <BR>
